@node Introduction "Gaussin Blur: Introduction"

                                  Introduction
                                 --------------

   Gaussian Blur is a plugin for the famous image-manipulation-program
   ArtEffect2/3+. As a normal PlugIn it integrates seamlessly in ArtEffect's
   menu and waits happily for your attention.

   Gaussian Blur is a high-speed and -quality implementation of a standard
   gaussian blur. Much much faster than ArtEffect2's and still twice as fast
   as ArtEffect3's new one.

@endnode

